headline: Humana Inc. to Release Third Quarter 2025 Results on November 5, 2025
summary: LOUISVILLE, Ky., October 10, 2025--Humana Inc. (NYSE: HUM) will release its financial results for the third quarter 2025 (3Q25), as well as prepared management remarks (in PDF format), at 6:00 a.m. Eastern time on November 5, 2025. The company will host a live question-and-answer session at 8:00 a.m. Eastern time that morning to discuss its financial results for the quarter and earnings guidance for 2025.

headline: Winners and losers from 2026 Medicare Advantage star ratings
summary: The CMS quietly released anticipated star ratings data Thursday night. Humana and Aetna saw enrollment in highly rated plans fall, while Elevance’s and Centene’s stars improved and UnitedHealthcare’s stayed stable.
